For more information about this project please see the following page:

http://www.hashbangcode.com/blog/zend-lucene-and-pdf-documents-part-1-pdf-meta-data-2081.html

To get the project up and running follow the following instructions:

1 Download Zend Framework from framework.zend.com and put the Zend directory into the library directory.
2 Open up the file application/configs/application.ini and change the references to your lucene and file directory locations.